-- EU Sets 2013 Carbon Cap at 2.039 Billion Metric Tons as Program Expands
-- B y   E w a   K r u k o w s k a   a n d   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 2010-10-22T09:54:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/eu-sets-2013-carbon-cap-at-2-039-billion-metric-tons-as-program-expands.html
The European Union said the 2013 cap
for carbon-dioxide discharges by energy and manufacturing
companies will be 2.039 billion metric tons, an adjustment to
reflect the expansion of the EU emissions-trading system to
include aluminum and chemical makers that year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
